cs.CL, cs.SI, cs.IR, cs.SD, cs.LG

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language processing and summarization of online dialogues. 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is also likely as the paper focuses on social media data and extracting information from it. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is relevant as the paper deals with identifying important segments of dialogues. 
- cs.SD (Software Engineering) could be relevant as the paper presents computational models for summarization. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also possible as the paper uses SVMs and Bidirectional LSTMs for feature extraction and classification.
